#: data/campaigns/Dead_Water/scenarios/02_Flight.cfg:80
msgid ""
"Move Kai Krellis to the north-west corner of the map. He must be level one "
"or higher."
msgstr "让凯·克莱利斯移动到地图的西北角。他必须升级到一级以上。"

